I.  System hierarchy
    LV0: Root       
        - Archive: memory interface, self-defined API
    LV1: Scheduler  
        - Plato: scheduling tasks
    LV2: Agent    
        - Demeter: spawning, collecting, building and managing
        - Minerva: scouting, defending and attacking
        - Hephaestus: manufacturing
        - Hermes: trading
    
